        {
          "question": "<p>Dissolve two spoons of common salt in half a cup of water. Now if you want to get the salt back, what will you do?</p>",
          "id": 315380,
          "options_data": [],
          "solution_data": [
            {
              "id": 203092,
              "solution": "<p>We can get back the salt we dissolved in water by two methods-</p>\n\n<ol start=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-roman;\">\n\t<li>Either heating up the salted water in a pan on a burner.</li>\n\t<li>Keeping the salted water pan in the sun.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>In both ways, the water will get evaporated in the form of water vapours and the salt will remain back in the pan.</p>"
