        {
          "question": "<p>Explain the process of rooftop rainwater harvesting with the help of a suitable diagram.</p>",
          "id": 315420,
          "options_data": [],
          "solution_data": [
            {
              "id": 203110,
              "solution": "<html><body><p>Rooftop water harvesting is a special technique used to conserve water. It is generally used in places where there is lack of water or water scarcity.<br/>\nIn this technique, rainwater is collected on the roof and through a pipe. The water is filtered because it may contain soil. Sometimes, the pipes are directly connected into the pits in the ground to recharge the groundwater for further use.<br/>\n<img alt=\"\" data-imgur-src=\"BAF0jYx.png\" src=\"https://media-mycbseguide.s3.amazonaws.com/images/imgur/BAF0jYx.png\" style=\"width: 250px; height: 173px;\"/></p></body></html>"
            }
          ],
